{"word":"H6005 - עִמָּנוּאֵל - ʻImmânûwʼêl - im-maw-noo-ale' - Immanuel","slug":"H6005","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עִמָּנוּאֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻImmânûwʼêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>im-maw-noo-ale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Immanuel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עמּנוּאל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛immânû'êl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>im-maw-noo-ale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Immanuel = \"God with us\" or \" with us is God\" <ol><li>symbolic and prophetic name of the Messiah, the Christ, prophesying that He would be born of a virgin and would be 'God with us'</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H5973\">H5973</a> and <a href=\"#/H410\">H410</a> with a pronominal suffix inserted <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:1640 - 'mm\">1640d</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5971\">H5971</a>, <a href=\"#/H5973\">H5973</a>, <a href=\"#/H5978\">H5978</a>, <a href=\"#/H5980\">H5980</a>, <a href=\"#/H5981\">H5981</a>, <a href=\"#/H5983\">H5983</a>, <a href=\"#/H5984\">H5984</a>, <a href=\"#/H5985\">H5985</a>, <a href=\"#/H5988\">H5988</a>, <a href=\"#/H5989\">H5989</a>, <a href=\"#/H5990\">H5990</a>, <a href=\"#/H5991\">H5991</a>, <a href=\"#/H5992\">H5992</a>, <a href=\"#/H5996\">H5996</a>"}]}